FAQ

What currencies does Empire Market support?

Bitcoin (BTC) and Monero (XMR) are main currencies.

Few more (list can change at any time): Litecoin, Binance coin, TetherUSDT, Tron, Doge coin, Ethereum.

Where can I buy Bitcoins?

Learn more at our Bitcoin guide page.

How does escrow work for digital listings?

Once you purchase the listing it will be marked as processing, the vendor has 12 hours to complete the order by sending the digital item then marking the order as shipped otherwise the order will be cancelled. Once the order has been marked as shipped the buyer can either finalize the order once they have received the purchase, dispute the order if there is a problem or extend escrow if required. If the buyer does nothing once the order is marked as shipped it will auto-finalize after being marked as shipped for 12 hours.

Can I use any escrow outside the Empire market?

No, it’s against the rules. We make 2% from every trade (escrow) and this money keeps running this service. Markets like this wouldn’t exist if we allowed any outside trades.

How can I become a vendor?

Read the information on the ‘BECOME A VENDOR’ page. You will need to follow the vendor rules and pay the vendor fee. All vendors will be tested and checked. Vendors are required to set up 2FA to secure their account. If you are caught scamming, padding feedback or breaking any other rule your vendor account will be revoked and you could be banned.

Are all listings done through escrow?

Yes!

I deposited twice to the same address?

System generates a new deposit address for every new deposit, if you send two deposits to the same address you will need to create a support ticket and request assistance. We can usually fix it easily.

How can I leave feedback for an order?

You can leave feedback any time at the product page.

What do I do if i’m experiencing a glitch or bug?

Create a support ticket and explain what is happening for you.

Why does the market page go blank sometimes?

This only happens if you are using the market on a mobile device. The market is only designed to be used on a PC. Make sure the Javascript is ON. It’s safe!

What do I do if i’ve been scammed?

Visit our Escrow page start dispute and explain the situation. To prevent being scammed you should fully utilize escrow, this means don’t finalize the order if you haven’t received it and dispute the order or extend the escrow if required.

When can I PM on the forum?

New users unlock the PM feature on the forum after a couple of days of activity.

Can I get a sample?

It’s not a nice gesture to ask for a sample. Most of our clients have 98-100% positive trades. Our team of experts have tested every seller before he is allowed to list items here. After your purchase if you aren’t happy with your item, start dispute process and money will be refunded.

Tracking:

Tracking will be given to you same day after purchase and can be found in your receipt and in the confirmation email you will receive.

Physical shipment:

Most of the vendors will ship package within 1 hour of receiving notification about payment into Escrow. DHL & UPS ship Monday-Friday and not during holidays. Vendors will ship with FEDEX Mon-Sat and any other delivery service you will mention during checkout process. You can ask for any if you want any special. FEDEX, DHL, UPS, MAIL packages will be mailed the same day.

Packaging & Labeling:

Small orders are shipped inside magazines or binders, Large orders are shipped in boxes with labeling to appear like an Ebay or Amazon.com package. Additional stealth precautions are taken that we don’t publicly share. Please let us know if you have special requirements.

Items via Emai:

(Gift Cards, Credit/Debit Cards, Transfers,etc):

Items sent via email do not require any identity information such as name, address, etc. You can enter random characters as an alternative. Client receives response within 1 – 3 hrs. If there is a case of mass digital goods orders, receiving your order may take up to 5hrs. We advise you to be patient as we will respond to you accordingly.
